533
00:34:20.920 --> 00:34:22.000
Real estate.

534
00:34:22.380 --> 00:34:24.210
Like a broker?

535
00:34:24.670 --> 00:34:26.840
You know. more like an investor.

536
00:34:27.710 --> 00:34:29.540
Well. I'd be working with the investors.

537
00:34:29.630 --> 00:34:30.460
Hand in hand.

538
00:34:30.540 --> 00:34:31.790
So. they're hiring you?

539
00:34:33.420 --> 00:34:34.460
Kind of a partnership.

540
00:34:35.630 --> 00:34:36.960
A partnership.

541
00:34:39.340 --> 00:34:41.960
- Susie.
- Yeah. yeah.

542
00:34:42.050 --> 00:34:43.670
- It's good to see you.
- You too.

543
00:34:54.670 --> 00:34:55.670
I'm in.

544
00:34:56.710 --> 00:34:57.710
You sure?

545
00:34:57.790 --> 00:35:00.210
