- Yeah.

554
00:35:33.920 --> 00:35:34.920
Good.

555
00:35:35.500 --> 00:35:36.540
You ever play golf?

556
00:35:37.000 --> 00:35:38.210
No.

557
00:35:38.290 --> 00:35:40.420
Well. before you learn
how to talk real estate.

558
00:35:40.500 --> 00:35:42.500
you gotta learn
how to talk to rich white folks

559
00:35:42.590 --> 00:35:44.250
so it seems like you one of 'em.

560
