563
00:35:52.170 --> 00:35:54.290
Yeah. I played
a lot of sports as a kid. So...

564
00:35:54.380 --> 00:35:56.500
So... yes?

565
00:35:56.590 --> 00:35:58.210
- Yes.
- All right. then.

566
