Take him over and get him outfitted.

567
00:36:00.420 --> 00:36:02.590
Show him the basics
and I'll take over from there.

568
00:36:02.670 --> 00:36:03.670
Follow me.

569
00:36:09.710 --> 00:36:11.090
So a hundred dollars to my one?

570
