You think it's a done deal because.
what. I'm such a good golf teacher?

571
00:36:15.250 --> 00:36:17.500
You can fake math.
You can't fake a golf game.

572
00:36:17.590 --> 00:36:18.840
He's right about that. Joe.

573
00:36:20.000 --> 00:36:23.210
Bernard. this is Don Silverthorne.
My banker.

574
00:36:23.290 --> 00:36:25.130
Flew all the way down
from San Francisco

575
00:36:25.210 --> 00:36:26.540
just to see how crazy we are.

576
00:36:26.630 --> 00:36:27.630
Nice to meet you.

577
00:36:30.710 --> 00:36:31.800
Shit!

578
00:36:31.880 --> 00:36:33.630
Well. it looks like I got my answer.

579
00:36:33.710 --> 00:36:35.500
Let's try that again.

580
00:36:35.590 --> 00:36:37.170
All right. What do I do differently?

581
00:36:37.250 --> 00:36:38.250
Swing lower.

582
00:36:38.840 --> 00:36:40.670
- Great. thanks.
- Keep your head still.

583
00:36:41.130 --> 00:36:42.420
Head still. head still...

584
00:36:45.540 --> 00:36:46.670
No. you moved.

585
00:36:47.340 --> 00:36:50.210
If this charade's gonna work
and you guys want me to finance.

586
00:36:50.290 --> 00:36:52.960
I just hope you don't offer
over two million for that building.

587
00:36:53.540 --> 00:36:55.090
More than that. I don't want the risk.

588
00:36:56.130 --> 00:36:58.290
I can get that building
for under two million.

589
